metrics-stack is a metapackage: it installs the full monitoring stack by
depending on the three component packages.

  metrics-stack-prometheus     Prometheus + alerting rules + monitoring-add-exporter
  metrics-stack-alertmanager   Alertmanager + monitoring-configure-email
  metrics-stack-grafana        Grafana + monitoring-add-dashboard
  metrics-stack-common         shared 'metrics' Podman network (pulled in by all three)

Each component package installs and runs standalone -- install just what a
host needs. Removing this metapackage does not remove the components;
remove (or purge, on Debian) the component packages themselves.

Project: https://github.com/baileyallison/metrics
